  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "=General= Görvälstorp is one of the smaller areas, with a number of established problems and a few projects. =Directions= 3 km north of Jägarhyddan on Route 280. Bus stop (639) Görvälstorp (by the greenhouses). From the bus stop, walk back 200 m to a small tractor track crossing the main road. Parking is available on the left. The track to the right leads to the boulders. Walk about 100 m; Stora blocket will then be visible on the left. Tandenblocket, Lilla stenen and Lutande stenen are nearby. Skogsblocket is about 50 m further into the woods. =Sectors=",
